def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = np.zeros_like(bins)
    mask = bins != max_capacity
    
    denom = bins - item
    denom[denom == 0] = 1

    return scores

def score(item, bins):
    max_capacity = np.max(bins)
    scores = np.where(bins == max_capacity, -1, item / bins)
    scores[bins - item <= 0] = 0
    return scores
